Make a log file showing APU writes so you can see if it's a bug with your APU or CPU/hardware. If it's writing 0 to $4015 when you pause the game, then it's clearly an APU bug since that should silence all channels. If it's not, are the length counters all getting set to 0?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=17">blargg</a> — Wed Dec 28, 2005 5:39 pm</p><hr />
